Dialogs.Text: SecurPink1850: A pleasure to meet you. New? There is more people here?
MsMaki95: Yeah, i make art for people in this server! ^o^
Thomas B: So those pictures i found back in that room were recent.
MsMaki95: I can make a drawing of your avatar if you want. n-n
SecurPink1850: Don't worry, there is no need yet, since i'm new here, i want to see if i keep this avatar.
SecurPink1850: But thanks for the offer.
MsMaki95: I understand, when you have an avatar that you like, you know where to find me. n-n
MsMaki95: Still, yours looks cool, gives a mysterious vibe! >-o
SecurPink1850: Mysterious? Well, it's kind of my style.
Thomas B: And the style of every person on the internet. With that judgement, i can tell she is not an AI for a place as old as this.
MsMaki95: Oh! Speaking of mysterious... o-o
